fixed-width-fontset package

This package provides fixed-width CJK fontsets for Carbon Emacs on Mac OS X
and Emacs on W32 called NTEmacs.

1. Usage

Mac OSX user
    Please read documentation in carbon-font.el

Windows user
    Please read documentation in ntemacs-font.el

2. files

Changelog               : previous Changelogs for carbon-font.el
carbon-font.el          : OS oriented variables are defined for Mac OSX.
fixed-width-fontset.el  : provide functions to create CJK fontsets and to adjust
                          face-font-rescale-alist automatically.
ntemacs-font.el         : OS oriented variables are defined for MS Windows.
ntemacs-font-sample.el  : Samples for fontset creation using fonts not
                          oriented from OS
readme                  : This file
readme.ja               : readme (ja)
    
